open it up to Q&amp;A.

00:31:43.609 --> 00:31:45.150
So if anyone has
any questions, there

00:31:45.150 --> 00:31:49.410
is a microphone over there.

00:31:49.410 --> 00:31:50.985
Not all at once, guys.

00:31:50.985 --> 00:31:51.860
AUDIENCE: Hey, there.

